<h2>Seller review request received</h2>

<p>A blocked seller has requested a manual review.</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Vendor:</strong> <%= vendorName %></li>
  <li><strong>Seller slug:</strong> <%= sellerSlug %></li>
  <li><strong>Requested by:</strong> <%= requestedByEmail || requestedBy %></li>
  <li><strong>Reason:</strong> <%= reasonLabel %></li>
  <% if (message) { %>
    <li><strong>Message:</strong> <%= message %></li>
  <% } %>
</ul>

<p style="margin-top: 16px;">
Open the seller dashboard admin area to approve or reject the request.
</p>
